==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fryer
<hw>Fry"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Something or someone
that fries.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A young chicken or other food item suitable to be
cooked by frying.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A pot equipped with a removable basket, designed to
be used for frying objects; -- also called <altname>deep
fryer</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frying</ent>⟦br⟧
